item.title: Fields for #495 Please
item.dc:creator: @BAsh_CntLgn BAsh(CntLgn)
item.description:
@BAsh_CntLgn wrote:

[quote=“belbn, post:6, topic:201181”]Thanks alot yak!

Mind telling me how you got these so i dont have to ask for future updates?[/quote]
Probably the same way everyone else does it. He hooks them with bcel. The only difference is that he probably hooks a lot more stuff to make sure that an individual hook will fail before it returns invalid stuff or simply take the most likely of these inputs. On top of that his updater has probably undergone several revisions with each update so that he only hooks stuff that doesn’t change.
